reviewText: Kids love both movies. Happy happy. The quality of the bluray is excellent! Highly recommend!
Great price for two awesome movies!
I got it for Rango so I'm pleased.  Watched Yogi Bear and was not that thrilled with that movie.
5 stars for Rango.  1 star for Yogi Bear.  Yogi's a stinker man.  I want the hour and a half of my life back for that one.  So yeah, you're buying this one solely for Rango.  Great flick.
Not great blockbuster movies, but definitely worth the $6 I paid for them. Kids friendly (Rango does have guns though).

Excellent value here, the BD of Rango contains both the theatrical and 5 minutes longer Directors cut and Yogi is a remake of the old TV offerings of 30 years ago and is as well done as the originals. In a dual pack this is good value, Rango is an absolutely outstanding film, one of the best animated films ever in my view.
havent watched yet but have seen both before  cant wait to watch again

Great movie.  My 4 year old would watch every day, multiple times a day if I would let him

Rango is weird and i love him.  Johnny Depp is so strange.  Yogi bear is terrible, voice is bad (sorry Dan) I couldn't do better but Yogi is hard to do, like Barney on the Flinstones.  Quality of Blu is good.  If you like weird and strange and good then this is for you.
